[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "开始下雪了。通讯也受到干扰——这都是泰坦物质污染的影响。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“树”的周围总是出现这样的情形。它仍是远在天边。银装素裹，身着绮幻。像朔州传说中的蓬莱仙境，似是碧玉乐土的终点。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "跳下驾驶室，脚下是松软的泥土和嫩绿的草。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_01",
        "zh_CN": "咦……达令！你看！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮把手伸到我面前——雪花落在她的手背上，融化成点点水痕。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是自然降雪，而不是泰坦物质污染催生的雪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "弯下腰，在小溪里捧起水。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "已经凉到有些割手了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（反常的降温。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "生命在凋零。用不了多久，青草会枯死，土地也会像石头一样硬，甚至连溪流都要冻起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "载具的效率也在降低。等温度降到零下之后，等积雪漫过膝盖，甚至没过腰之后，它们恐怕也走不了多远了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抬起头，再次看向远处的“树”。树冠正簇着一团深色的云，一路蔓延向我们所在的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一闪而过的错觉——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那棵“树”正在注视、敌视着我，恐惧、拒绝着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮在我旁边站定。她和我一同望着一路延伸而来的乌云，皱着眉头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但很快，她就又踌躇满志地拉住我——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_02",
        "zh_CN": "达令，你看！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_03",
        "zh_CN": "指向这里的乌云，多像是我们的征途！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_04",
        "zh_CN": "啊，你的手好冰……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她把我的手捧在脸前呵着气。我摸了摸她的脑袋，招呼上其他队员，围在一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我打算分兵。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 1,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_05",
        "zh_CN": "哦？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "气温开始往下掉了。我们带着这么多物资和设备，后面光是低温情况下的故障问题就处理不完。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "特别是用来应对集群作战的战斗载具和火力支援模块，丢掉它们只是时间问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 3,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_01",
        "zh_CN": "能耗也是个问题。温度再降些的话，这些就都成了累赘。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没错。等积雪厚起来之后，我们要建立一个临时营地，并分一个人驻扎在那儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我会带走大部分燃料，只留下火力支援模块的空投消耗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所谓火力支援模块，既可以使用大口径武器远程支援，又可以空投重型武器模组，为轻装作战的单位提供对群作战能力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl002_01",
        "zh_CN": "那就是说，一旦遇到大规模的敌人，就会很难处理了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "用机动性绕过它们。抛下这些大块头，我们就很难被缠上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 3,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_02",
        "zh_CN": "这样倒也可以。但到“树”下的时候，我们就会少一个人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不会。在通讯完全中断之前，留守的人就要赶过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以……留守的人选。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 1,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_06",
        "zh_CN": "我！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 1,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_07",
        "zh_CN": "虽然很想一直和你一起战斗……但这种最危险的任务，就交给我好了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙也往前走了一步。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl002_02",
        "zh_CN": "你需要我在哪里，我就在哪里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
