        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我皱着眉。似乎有什么东西吸引着这些异化人，源源不断地向我们发起攻击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是“树”吗？气温骤降也是它的杰作吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果是，为什么不等到气温再低一些、环境再有利一些？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "异化人潮还是看不到尽头。它们从土里爬出来、从山坡下爬上来。那种熟悉感——感知中的泰坦力量仍然存在，丝毫没有减弱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "雪开始变大了。乌云铺到了头顶，凝得天色都暗了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_12",
        "zh_CN": "什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有泰坦藏在这里。里芙！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不需要更多描述，里芙便领会了我的意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "湛蓝色的光辉从她身上散开。环状光晕的逸散似乎连带着时间都迟钝、凝滞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "万事万物、万类万象，此刻都逃不过她的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl002_04",
        "zh_CN": "出来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "电流从她身上迸射而出，如瀑布般溅落在地上，顺着一切可能穿透的缝隙跃进。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下一刻，大地开始颤动——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有东西藏在下面！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl008_13",
        "zh_CN": "我来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮高举右手，金色的光芒在手上汇聚。丘陵上宛若点起一颗新星，照得乌云四散，连空中飘着的雪都消弭不见了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那团光芒在她的手中止不住跃动。而后，像是烈日沉入海的彼端，又像倾泻的金属射流——光柱轰击向脚下的大地，岩石和泥块遮蔽了天地，却遮不住哪怕一缕光芒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "丘陵被剖开了。芬妮开出了一道数十米深的坑洞。在碎石之间，泰坦的半边身子熔成暗红色，却还挣扎着站起身，用残存的肢体，想要向上攀爬。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮的左手开始凝聚第二次攻击。我抬了抬手，制止了她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不用了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一道灰色一闪而逝。泰坦的机体开始崩坏，露出身后的安卡希雅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我回过头，异化人已经恢复了平日那种低机能的状态——漫无目的地原地游荡。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "被芬妮的光芒破开的乌云，又厚厚地叠了回来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凝视着“树”，直到一团似有意似无意的白雾隔绝了视线，把“树”完全裹了起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "走吧，雪又大了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天黑到再也分辨不出乌云的边缘。我们建设好临时营地，布置好哨塔，准备休息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "前半夜是芬妮值守，后半夜是里芙。安卡希雅需要独自行动，所以要优先保证她的休息时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我坐在床边，看着地图。安卡希雅在身后躺着，里芙则坐在我对面。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "按降雪量来看，至少还有四天的路程。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙没有接话，看了看窗外的雪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "实际情况只会更加严峻。物资，设备，积雪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl002_05",
        "zh_CN": "还有异化人和泰坦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……没错。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我总有种直觉——“树”在畏惧我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它知道我想干什么——找到它，杀掉它。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "摊开手掌，看着掌心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我拥有的力量，独一无二的力量——拔除“树”的力量。我可以吸收并转换泰坦物质，可以说是“树”的天敌。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埋在路上的泰坦，漫山遍野的异化人，一直拢在头顶的阴云。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这都是它设置的阻碍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_11",
        "zh_CN": "要走“邪道”吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "邪道——游戏中利用漏洞，从而跳过困难关卡的方式。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你没睡？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 118,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_12",
        "zh_CN": "熬夜熬多了，这会儿还不困。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 119,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她爬起来，伏在桌子前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 120,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_13",
        "zh_CN": "我们只会越走越慢。如果像你感觉的那样，“树”真的在阻拦我们的话……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 121,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_14",
        "zh_CN": "那这就是个塔防游戏了。拖得越久，路上就会出现各种玉米射手和爆裂南瓜守卫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 122,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我也是这么想的。所以，我想换条路线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 123,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在显示屏上画了一条弧线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 124,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我打算从这里——直接走水路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_15",
        "zh_CN": "那物资怎么办？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "影响速度的，全都抛下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_16",
        "zh_CN": "走着去？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 128,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl002_06",
        "zh_CN": "不用看我。你知道的，我没意见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 131,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在通讯断开之前，还可以空投一轮物资。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 132,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "够快的话，两天就能到。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 133,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_17",
        "zh_CN": "那就没有退路咯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 134,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "无所谓了，本来就没有。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 135,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从上次踏足朔州开始，这棵“树”就像受了刺激一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 136,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "放任不管的话，它迟早要把朔州变成死境。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅辉夜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep2_girl001_18",
        "zh_CN": "好了，决定了就快睡觉。里芙还要值后半夜呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "留下一盏灯，抱着她，窸窣着钻进被窝里。温度已经降到了零下，身上却暖暖的——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "背后是里芙在抱我。空着的右手反手牵住了她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "睡意渐浓，外面寒风呼啸。不知过了多久，身边突然空了一块，然后填进来一个冰冰凉凉的感受。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 142,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是芬妮回来了。半梦半醒之间，下意识抱着她，用体温裹着她，抚着她的头发，直到她的呼吸也变得均匀。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 143,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "雪还在下。我很快又睡着了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 144,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天蒙蒙亮。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 145,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "安卡希雅和芬妮挤在我怀里，睡得很不安生。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 146,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从她们中间抽身出来——里芙还在外面。披上衣服走出帐篷，抬起头，对上里芙的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 147,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
